sequenceDiagram
    participant CP as Charge Point (OCTT)
    participant CS as Central System (SUT)

    Note over CP,CS: TC_019_2_CSMS: Retrieve specific configuration key
    Note over CP,CS: Section 3.7.2 - Core Profile - Configuration Happy Flow

    CS->>CP: 1. GetConfiguration.req (key = SupportedFeatureProfiles)

    CP-->>CS: 2. GetConfiguration.conf (configurationKey.key = SupportedFeatureProfiles)

    Note over CP,CS: Validation: unknownKey list MUST be empty<br/>configurationKey.key should be "SupportedFeatureProfiles"<br/>(NOTE: doc uses "should be", treating as MUST for test)
